- subscribed_already = user_signed_in? && current_user.subscribed?

%h1 Donations &amp; Sponsorships

%div{ style: "max-width: 60em;" }

  %p.py-2
    If you find Tiddlyhost useful then please consider a donation or a
    sponsorship. A donation or sponsorship will help cover hosting costs, and
    encourage the continued support and development of Tiddlyhost.

  %p.py-2
    Click the buttons below to donate or sponsor via
    = link_to('PayPal', "https://www.paypal.com/", target: '_blank', style: "padding-left: 0.25em;") + ','
    = link_to('Github Sponsors', "https://github.com/sponsors", target: '_blank', style: "padding-left: 0.25em;") + ','
    or
    = link_to('Buy Me a Coffee', "https://www.buymeacoffee.com/", style: "padding-left: 0.25em;") + '.'

  %p.py-2
    You can also now subscribe to the <b>Tiddlyhost Standard</b> plan,
    which gives you access to additional Tiddlyhost features, as well
    as supports the continued development of Tiddlyhost.
    Visit
    = link_to bi_icon('bag-check', style: 'margin-right: 0px;') + 'Subscriptions', '/subscription',
      style: "padding: 0.25em;"
    to learn more about Tiddlyhost subscription plans.
    - if subscribed_already
      %sup.th-dim
        &dagger;

  %p.py-2
    .donate-button
      = render 'paypal_donate_button'

    .donate-button{ style: 'margin-top: 1.9em;' }
      = render 'github_sponsor_button'

    .donate-button{ style: 'margin-top: 1.9em; padding-left:4px;' }
      = link_to "https://www.buymeacoffee.com/simonbaird", title: 'Buy Me a Coffee', target: '_blank' do
        = image_tag "coffee.svg", style: "width: 120px;"

    .donate-button.ms-2
      = link_to '/subscription' do
        = bi_icon('bag-check', style: 'margin-right: 3px;') + 'Subscriptions'


  - if subscribed_already
    %p.py-4.th-text-small.th-dim
      &dagger;&nbsp; I can see you're already a subscriber. Thank you very much!
